ibis.ipl.impl

Class ReadMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • ibis.ipl.impl.ReadMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ibis.ipl.ReadMessage

    public class ReadMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements ibis.ipl.ReadMessage
    Implementation of the ReadMessage interface. This is a complete implementation, but may be extended by an implementation. In that case, the ReceivePort.createReadMessage(SerializationInput, ReceivePortConnectionInfo) method must also be redefined.
